title: Stop what you're doing and watch these 4 shows!
text:
Stop What You're Doing And Watch These 4 Shows Now! Katherine Biek, Eugene Daniels 8:16 PM, Oct 3, 2015 
TV's fall premiere season is upon us (finally!) and sometimes sifting through the new pilots is basically impossible. So, we watched every single brand spanking new show for you and chose a few that you should definitely tune into as soon as possible. 
This video includes images from Fox .
